data.description: ***OPEN HOUSE!!! Open house Sunday, October 29, 12pm-2pm***  Home qualifies for 100% Financing with USDA! Fantastic 3 bedroom/2 bath in Oakridge West. Cathedral ceiling  in living room. Beautiful eat-in kitchen with bay window has gorgeous cabinets and solid counters, stainless  appliances, hardwood floors, and crown molding. Fridge to remain. Nice master with trey ceiling, walk-in  closet, double vanity, garden tub, and separate shower in master bath. Bed 3 has hardwood floors, French  Doors, and built-in bookcase. Huge yard, back patio and deck, double garage, and front porch finish out this  brick home. Don't delay...Call your agent to schedule an appointment today!
